PrecisLeasing to the Province of NEW BRUNSWICK, for a term of forty-nine years, of an additional 6,000 square metres of land situate at the Fredericton Research Station in the City of Fredericton, New Brunswick, which are to be used as the site for the construction of a two-storey addition to the existing provincial office building.
